See what's happening at mountains across Australia from your phone with ease!
AusSnowCam provides you with a simple interface to quickly browse snow cams of various snow resorts in Australia.

Currently supports the following resorts
-Mt Buller
-Mt Hotham
-Falls Creek

This app is not affiliated with Mt Buller, Mt Hotham or Falls Creek. All images are copyright to their respective owners.

Version 1.0
-Initial release
-Supports Mt Buller, Mt Hotham and Falls Creek

Version 1.1
-Small screen support